
Project Name: CSX Scanner
Author:       Chen Liu
Email:        chenliu@uky.edu


1.Description:
This project implements the scanner module for the programming language CSX.
Use the JFlex scanner-generation tool(based on Lex).



2.Instruction to compile the program:

   make

The command above compiles or recomplies classes. The ".class" files are placed
in subdirectory classes.



3.Instruction to run the program:

   make test

The command above will run the program, and the default input file is test.csx.
However, you could also redirect the input file through command:

   make test INPUTFILE=newfilename


